#: likertplot/results/helpMessage.content
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<style> .block { border: 2px solid gray; border-radius: 15px; background-color: WhiteSmoke; padding: 0px 20px; text-align: justify; } </style> <div class=\"block\"> <h2>Likert Plot Help</h2> <h3>Data & Sorting</h3>\n"
"<ul> <li>Likert variables must be of ordinal measure-type. (Continuous measure-type works as well.)</li> <li>If you plan to compute mean/median/sd or to use comparison tests, they must be of integer data-type.</li> <li><strong>Tidy up levels:</strong> when checked, try to fix the labels order in table and graph (when some variables miss some levels).</li> <li><strong>Convert variables to integer:</strong> when checked, the level labels are ignored and only integer values are used.</li> <li><strong>Sort Variables by Median:</strong> orders the list of Likert variables by median.</li> </ul>\n"
"<h3>Comparison Tests</h3> When using a group variable, several tests are available: <ul> <li><strong>Mann-Whitney U:</strong> Two group comparison</li> <li><strong>Kruskal-Wallis:</strong> n group comparison</li> <li><strong>Post Hoc Tests:</strong> Dunn, Conover and Dwass-Steel-Critchlow-Fligner (DSCF) paiwise comparisons tests.</li> </ul>\n"
"<p>p-Values can be adjusted <strong>groupwise</strong> (for each question) for post hoc tests or <strong>overall</strong> (groupwise and questionwise) for MannWithney U, Kruskal-Wallis and post hoc tests. DSCF p-values are already adjusted (groupwise); no other adjustment is possible.</p> </div>"
msgstr ""
"<style> .block { border: 2px solid gray; border-radius: 15px; background-color: WhiteSmoke; padding: 0px 20px; text-align: justify; } </style> <div class=\"block\"> <h2>Likert Plot 帮助</h2> <h3>数据和排序</h3>\n"
"<ul> <li>Likert 变量必须是有序测量类型。 (连续测量类型也可以。)</li> <li>如果您计划计算均值/中位数/标准差或使用比较测试，则它们必须是整数数据类型。</li> <li><strong>整理级别：</strong> 当选中时，尝试在表格和图表中修复标签顺序（当某些变量缺少某些级别时）。</li> <li><strong>将变量转换为整数：</strong> 当选中时，会忽略级别标签，只使用整数值。</li> <li><strong>按中位数排序变量：</strong> 按中位数顺序排列 Likert 变量列表。</li> </ul>\n"
"<h3>比较测试</h3> 使用组变量时，有几种测试可用： <ul> <li><strong>Mann-Whitney U：</strong> 两个组的比较</li> <li><strong>Kruskal-Wallis：</strong> n 组比较</li> <li><strong>事后测试：</strong> Dunn、Conover 和 Dwass-Steel-Critchlow-Fligner (DSCF) 成对比较测试。</li> </ul>\n"
"<p>p 值可以按 <strong>组</strong> （对于每个问题）进行事后测试的调整，或按 <strong>整体</strong> （组和问题）进行 Mann-Whitney U、Kruskal-Wallis 和事后测试的调整。DSCF p 值已经按组调整；不可能进行其他调整。</p> </div>"

#: corresp/results/helpMessage.content
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<style> .block { border: 2px solid gray; border-radius: 15px; background-color: WhiteSmoke; padding: 0px 20px; text-align: justify; } </style> <div class=\"block\"> <p><strong>Correspondence Plot Help</strong></p>\n"
"<p>This module computes <strong>Correspondence Analysis (CA)</strong> for two categorical variables. Computations are based on <a href = \"https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=FactoMineR\" target=\"_blank\">FactoMineR<a/> package by F.&nbsp;Husson, J.&nbsp;Josse, S.&nbsp;Le, J.&nbsp;Mazet.</p>\n"
"<p>The data may be weighted using <em>jamovi</em> built-in weight system or using the \"Counts\" variable.</p>\n"
"<p><strong>Supplementary row or column</strong> numbers may be entered as integer lists : 1,3,6</p>\n"
"<p>Four normalizations (scaling of row and column scores before plotting) are avalaible : <ul> <li><strong>Principal:</strong> Row an columns scores are scaled by eigenvalues.</li> <li><strong>Symetric:</strong> Row an columns scores are scaled by the square root of eigenvalues. </li> <li><strong>Row Principal:</strong> Only row scores are scaled by eigenvalues.</li> <li><strong>Column Principal:</strong> Only column scores are scaled by eigenvalues.</li> <li><strong>Standard:</strong> The raw coordinates without normalization.</li> </ul></p>\n"
"<p>A sample file is included at Open > Data Library > vijPlots > Smoking</p>\n"
"</div>"
msgstr ""
"<style> .block { border: 2px solid gray; border-radius: 15px; background-color: WhiteSmoke; padding: 0px 20px; text-align: justify; } </style> <div class=\"block\"> <p><strong>对应图像帮助</strong></p>\n"
"<p>此模块计算 <strong>对应分析 (CA)</strong> 二个分类变量。 计算栖为 <a href = \"https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=FactoMineR\" target=\"_blank\">FactoMineR<a/> 包作。</p>\n"
"<p>数据可以使用 <em>jamovi</em> 内置权重系统 或者使用 「数量」 变量。</p>\n"
"<p><strong>附加行或列</strong> 号数可以作为数字列表 : 1,3,6</p>\n"
"<p>在上是最多三种标准。 <ul> <li><strong>主题标准：</strong> 行和列分债分为给一个标准债。</li> <li><strong>简三标准：</strong> 行和列分债分为给一个标准债的二别前债。 </li> <li><strong>行主题标准：</strong> 只有行分债分为给一个标准债。</li> <li><strong>列主题标准：</strong> 只有列分债分为给一个标准债。</li> <li><strong>标准债：</strong> 本消体数据。</li> </ul></p>\n"
"<p>浏览文件包含在 Open > Data Library > vijPlots > Smoking</p>\n"
"</div>"

#: multcorresp/results/helpMessage.content
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<style> .block { border: 2px solid gray; border-radius: 15px; background-color: WhiteSmoke; padding: 0px 20px; text-align: justify; } </style> <div class=\"block\"> <p><strong>Multiple Correspondence Analysis Help</strong></p>\n"
"<p>This module computes <strong>Multiple Correspondence Analysis (MCA)</strong> for several categorical variables. Computations are based on <a href = \"https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=FactoMineR\" target=\"_blank\">FactoMineR<a/> package by F.&nbsp;Husson, J.&nbsp;Josse, S.&nbsp;Le, J.&nbsp;Mazet.</p>\n"
"<p>Both classic methods are available: <ul> <li><strong>Indicator matrix:</strong> CA of the indicator matrix</li> <li><strong>Burt matrix:</strong> CA of the Burt matrix. The eigenvalues are the squares of those of the indicator matrix method. </li> </ul> </p>\n"
"<p>Both methods give the same <em>standard</em> coordinates (but different <em>principal</em> coordinates).</p>\n"
"<p>When selected, <strong>Benzécri and Greenacre corrections</strong> are applied to eigenvalues only (<strong>Summary</strong> table). Coordinates (and inertia) of categories and observations are computed from the original eigenvalues of the Burt matrix.</p>\n"
"<p>The <strong>Normalization</strong> options specify how the coordinates are scaled (by eigenvalues): <ul> <li><strong>Principal:</strong> Both category and observation coordinates are scaled.</li> <li><strong>Category principal:</strong> Only category coordinates are scaled.</li> <li><strong>Observation principal:</strong> Only observation coordinates are scaled.</li> <li><strong>Standard:</strong> Both category and observation coordinates are standard.</li> </ul></p>\n"
"<p>A sample file is included at Open > Data Library > vijPlots > Cars</p>\n"
"</div>"
msgstr ""
"<style> .block { border: 2px solid gray; border-radius: 15px; background-color: WhiteSmoke; padding: 0px 20px; text-align: justify; } </style> <div class=\"block\"> <p><strong>多重對應分析說明</strong></p>\n"
"<p>此模組計算 <strong>多重對應分析 (MCA)</strong> 的數個分類變數。計算基於 <a href = \"https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=FactoMineR\" target=\"_blank\">FactoMineR<a/> 包由 F.&nbsp;Husson, J.&nbsp;Josse, S.&nbsp;Le, J.&nbsp;Mazet.</p>\n"
"<p>兩種經典方法都可用： <ul> <li><strong>指標矩陣：</strong> CA 的指標矩陣</li> <li><strong>Burt 矩陣：</strong> CA 的 Burt 矩陣。特徵值是指標矩陣方法的平方。 </li> </ul> </p>\n"
"<p>兩種方法都給出相同的 <em>標準</em> 坐標（但不同 <em>主</em> 坐標）。</p>\n"
"<p>當選擇時，<strong>Benzécri 和 Greenacre 校正</strong> 只適用於特徵值（<strong>摘要</strong> 表）。類別和觀察的坐標（和慣量）是從 Burt 矩陣的原始特徵值計算得出。</p>\n"
"<p><strong>標準化</strong> 選項指定坐標的縮放方式（按特徵值）： <ul> <li><strong>主：</strong> 類別和觀察的坐標都進行縮放。</li> <li><strong>類別主：</strong> 只有類別坐標進行縮放。</li> <li><strong>觀察主：</strong> 只有觀察坐標進行縮放。</li> <li><strong>標準：</strong> 類別和觀察的坐標都標準化。</li> </ul></p>\n"
"<p>示範檔案包含在 Open > Data Library > vijPlots > Cars</p>\n"
"</div>"

#: mrcrosstabs/results/helpMessage.content
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<style> .block { border: 2px solid gray; border-radius: 15px; background-color: WhiteSmoke; padding: 0px 20px; text-align: justify; } </style> <div class=\"block\"> <p><strong>Multiple Response Crosstab Help</strong></p>\n"
"<p>This module computes crosstab frequencies for multiple response questions, also known as \"Check All That Apply\" (CATA) questions.</p>\n"
"<p>Questions may be coded as : <ul> <li>several <strong>dummy (or indicator) variables</strong> using 0/1 or 1/2 for each possible answer</li> <li>a single <strong>multi-valued variable</strong> containing the checked answers, separated by a symbol (usually \",\" or \";\").</li> </ul></p>\n"
"<p>A sample file is included at Open > Data Library > vijPlots > Credit Cards</p>\n"
"</div>"
msgstr ""
"<style> .block { border: 2px solid gray; border-radius: 15px; background-color: WhiteSmoke; padding: 0px 20px; text-align: justify; } </style> <div class=\"block\"> <p><strong>多一回应答表帮助</strong></p>\n"
"<p>此模块计算 多一回应答表高量。</p>\n"
"<p>问题可以编码为 : <ul> <li>多个 <strong>棒字 (or 指示) 变量</strong> 使用 0/1 或 1/2 以为每个可能答结。</li> <li>一个 <strong>多债变量</strong> 包含选中答结。</li> </ul></p>\n"
"<p>浏览文件包含在 Open > Data Library > vijPlots > Credit Cards</p>\n"
"</div>"

#: mrfrequencies/results/helpMessage.content
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<style> .block { border: 2px solid gray; border-radius: 15px; background-color: WhiteSmoke; padding: 0px 20px; text-align: justify; } </style> <div class=\"block\"> <p><strong>Multiple Response Frequencies Help</strong></p>\n"
"<p>This module computes frequencies for multiple response questions, also known as \"Check All That Apply\" (CATA) questions.</p>\n"
"<p>Questions may be coded as : <ul> <li>several <strong>dummy (or indicator) variables</strong> using 0/1 or 1/2 for each possible answer</li> <li>a single <strong>multi-valued variable</strong> containing the checked answers, separated by a symbol (usually \",\" or \";\").</li> </ul></p>\n"
"<p>A sample file is included at Open > Data Library > vijPlots > Credit Cards</p>\n"
"</div>"
msgstr ""
"<style> .block { border: 2px solid gray; border-radius: 15px; background-color: WhiteSmoke; padding: 0px 20px; text-align: justify; } </style> <div class=\"block\"> <p><strong>多选项流行债分为帮助</strong></p>\n"
"<p>此模式计算多选项题的债分为。一个例子文件已在 Open > 数据库徵 > vijPlots > 修改卡中</p>\n"
"<p>问题可以被编码为 : <ul> <li>多个当为代表受信感。</li> <li>一个多债序受信感。</li> </ul></p>\n"
"</div>"

#: principal/results/helpMessage.content
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<style> .block { border: 2px solid gray; border-radius: 15px; background-color: WhiteSmoke; padding: 0px 20px; text-align: justify; } </style> <div class=\"block\"> <p><strong>Principal Component Analysis Help</strong></p>\n"
"<p>This module computes <strong>Principal Component Analysis (PCA)</strong> for several continuous variables. Computations are based on <tt>stats::prcomp</tt> function.</p>\n"
"<p>Although rotated components are not principal components, they are widely used. Only orthogonal rotations are available (from GPArotation package).</p>\n"
"<p>Loadings (variable coordinates) and scores (observation coordinates) are principal (scaled by the squareroot of eigenvalues).\n"
"<p>Biplot follows \"Biplots in Practice\" [Michael Greenacre, 2010]: <ul> <li><strong>Form biplot:</strong> Scores are principal (scaled by eigenvalues) while loadings are standard.</li> <li><strong>Covariance biplot:</strong> Loadings are principal while scores are standard. </li> </ul></p>\n"
"<p><strong>Advanced options</strong>: <ul> <li><strong>Standardize loadings:</strong> loadings are normalized with sums of squared equal to 1 (instead of eigenvalues)</li> <li><strong>Standardize scores:</strong> scores are normalized with variances equal to 1 (instead of eigenvalues)</li> <li><strong>Rotate eigenvectors:</strong> the rotation (varimax, etc) is applied to eigenvectors (standard loadings) instead of principal loadings (Stata way).</li> </ul> </p>\n"
"<p>A sample file is included at Open > Data Library > vijPlots > Iris</p>\n"
"</div>"
msgstr ""
"<style> .block { border: 2px solid gray; border-radius: 15px; background-color: WhiteSmoke; padding: 0px 20px; text-align: justify; } </style> <div class=\"block\"> <p><strong>主行编角帮助</strong></p>\n"
"<p>此模块计筗主行编角器片 (〈PCA〉) 与多个纯纯发量。 计筗为于 <tt>stats::prcomp</tt> 函数。</p>\n"
"<p>能一起行编角对象不是主行编角。 不过对于象都使用。 只有横行编角 (之于 GPArotation 包。)</p>\n"
"<p>负載 (发量当鷴) 和 警告 (目录当鷴) 都为主行编角 (分为二並平均债)。\n"
"<p>Biplots 以为 “Biplots in Practice” [Michael Greenacre, 2010]: <ul> <li><strong>形成 biplot:</strong> 警告为主行 (分为二並平均债) 和 负載为标准。</li> <li><strong>对续 biplot:</strong> 负載为主行 和 警告为标准 。 </li> </ul></p>\n"
"<p><strong>高级选项</strong>: <ul> <li><strong>标准负載:</strong> 负載为标准化于一 (及于二並平均债)</li> <li><strong>标准警告:</strong> 警告为标准化于一 (及于二並平均债)</li> <li><strong>改量谁組:</strong> 改量 (比如 varimax) 被用于谁組 (标准负載) 。</li> </ul> </p>\n"
"<p>测试文件可以在 Open > 数据库弹 > vijPlots > Iris</p>\n"
"</div>"

#: qqplot/results/helpMessage.content
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<style> .block { border: 2px solid gray; border-radius: 15px; background-color: WhiteSmoke; padding: 0px 20px; text-align: justify; } </style> <div class=\"block\"> <p><strong>QQ & PP Plots Help</strong></p>\n"
"<p>This module uses <a href = \"https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=qqplotr\" target=\"_blank\">qqplotr R package<a/> by Alexandre Almeida, Adam Loy and Heike Hofmann. In-depth information can be found in the package documentation on CRAN site.</p>\n"
"<p><strong>Reference line:</strong> Draws either the <em>identity line</em> (y = x) or the commonly-used <em>Q-Q line</em> that intercepts two data quantiles (Q<sub>0.25</sub> and Q<sub>0.75</sub>). P-P plot only supports identity line.</p>\n"
"<p><strong>Confidence band:</strong> Draws a confidence band around the reference line. qqplotr package provides several methods to compute the confidence band : <ul> <li><strong><em>Pointwise</em></strong> constructs pointwise confidence bands based on Normal confidence intervals;</li> <li><strong><em>Bootstrap</em></strong> creates pointwise confidence bands based on a parametric bootstrap;</li> <li><strong><em>Kolmogorov-Smirnov</em></strong> band is based on the Kolmogorov-Smirnov test;</li> <li><strong><em>Tail-Sensitive</em></strong> constructs a tail-sensitive confidence bands but is only implemented for Normal Q-Q plots;</li> <li><strong><em>Equal Local Levels (ELL)</em></strong> constructs simultaneous bands using the equal local levels.</li> </ul> P-P plots only support \"ELL\" and \"Bootstrap\" methods. </p>\n"
"<p><strong>Detrended plot:</strong> The objects are <em>detrended</em> according to the reference line. This procedure may help reducing visual bias caused by the orthogonal distances from the points to the reference line. </p>\n"
"<p><strong>Parameter values:</strong> The distribution parameters can be estimated from data using <ul> <li><strong>Maximum Likelihood Method</strong> (using MASS package) : it should work with all distributions but \"t\" and \"uniform\";</li> <li><strong>Method of Moments</strong> for moment based parameters : it should work with \"normal\", \"log-normal\", \"Beta\", \"Exponential\", \"Gamma\", \"Logistic\", \"Uniform\";</li> </ul> or entered by user: <ul> <li><strong>Parameter 1:</strong> : mean (Normal), meanlog (Log-normal), shape1 (Beta), location (Cauchy, Logistic), df (Chi-squared, Student), df1 (F), rate (Exponential), shape (Gamma, Weibull) and min (Uniform);</li> <li><strong>Parameter 2:</strong> : sd (normal), sdlog (Log-normal), shape2 (Beta), scale (Cauchy, Logistic), df2 (F), rate (Gamma, Weibull) and max (Uniform).</li> </ul> </p>\n"
"</div>"
msgstr ""
"<style> .block { border: 2px solid gray; border-radius: 15px; background-color: WhiteSmoke; padding: 0px 20px; text-align: justify; } </style> <div class=\"block\"> <p><strong>QQ & PP 圖表說明</strong></p>\n"
"<p>此模組使用 <a href = \"https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=qqplotr\" target=\"_blank\">qqplotr R 套件<a/> 由 Alexandre Almeida, Adam Loy 和 Heike Hofmann 開發。詳細資訊可在 CRAN 網站的套件文件中找到。</p>\n"
"<p><strong>參考線:</strong> 繪製 <em>身份線</em> (y = x) 或常用的 <em>Q-Q 線</em>，該線截斷兩個數據量級 (Q<sub>0.25</sub> 和 Q<sub>0.75</sub>)。P-P 圖表僅支援身份線。</p>\n"
"<p><strong>信賴帶:</strong> 繪製參考線周圍的信賴帶。qqplotr 套件提供多種方法計算信賴帶：<ul> <li><strong><em>點對點</em></strong> 基於 Normal 信賴區間構建點對點信賴帶；</li> <li><strong><em>自舉法</em></strong> 基於參數自舉法構建點對點信賴帶；</li> <li><strong><em>Kolmogorov-Smirnov</em></strong> 帶基於 Kolmogorov-Smirnov 測試；</li> <li><strong><em>尾敏感</em></strong> 構建尾敏感信賴帶，但僅實現於 Normal Q-Q 圖表；</li> <li><strong><em>等局部水平 (ELL)</em></strong> 構建同時帶使用等局部水平。</li> </ul> P-P 圖表僅支援 \"ELL\" 和 \"自舉法\" 方法。 </p>\n"
"<p><strong>去趨勢圖:</strong> 物體根據參考線 <em>去趨勢</em>。此程序可能有助於減少由點到參考線的正交距離引起的視覺偏差。 </p>\n"
"<p><strong>參數值:</strong> 分佈參數可以使用 <ul> <li><strong>最大似然法</strong> (使用 MASS 套件)：它應該適用於所有分佈，但 \"t\" 和 \"uniform\"；</li> <li><strong>矩法</strong> 進行基於矩的參數：它應該適用於 \"normal\"、\"log-normal\"、\"Beta\"、\"Exponential\"、\"Gamma\"、\"Logistic\" 和 \"Uniform\"；</li> </ul> 或由用戶輸入：<ul> <li><strong>參數 1:</strong>：均值 (Normal)、均值對數 (Log-normal)、形狀 1 (Beta)、位置 (Cauchy、Logistic)、自由度 (Chi-squared、Student)、自由度 1 (F)、速率 (Exponential)、形狀 (Gamma、Weibull) 和最小值 (Uniform)；</li> <li><strong>參數 2:</strong>：標準差 (normal)、標準差對數 (Log-normal)、形狀 2 (Beta)、尺度 (Cauchy、Logistic)、自由度 2 (F)、速率 (Gamma、Weibull) 和最大值 (Uniform)。</li> </ul> </p>\n"
"</div>"

