#: package.description
msgid ""
"Main statistical charts (histogram, boxplot, point, bar, line, raincloud…) "
"with many options along with Likert plot, multiple response barplot, "
"Principal Component and (Multiple) Correspondence Analyses. Project source "
"(and changelog) is available at <a "
"href=\"https://github.com/vjalby/vijPlots\" target=\"_blank\">Github</a>."
msgstr ""
"主要統計圖表（直方圖、箱形圖、點圖、長條圖、折線圖、雨雲圖等）搭配多種選項，"
"另提供李克特圖、多重回應長條圖、主成分分析與（多重）對應分析。專案原始碼與更"
"新紀錄請見 <a href=\"https://github.com/vjalby/vijPlots\" target=\"_blank\">"
"Github</a>."

